{"title":"主席话儿记心上","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":2,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席话儿记心上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象心头出太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席著作枕旁放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛闭上心里亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时刻想着主席话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象心头出太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席语录桌上放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我象身在主席旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身温暖心窝热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天增添新力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席话儿记心上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头脑清醒眼光亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心怀全球看得远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀山火海无阻挡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席著作天天学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断哺育我成长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辈子献身于革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百折不回永向上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学了“两论”心生亮学了“两论”心生亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"困难一脚踢个光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甩掉石油落后帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千斤重担敢承担！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早听早自由要想井听人的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人先要听毛主席的话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早听毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管井就早自由；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚听毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管井就晚自由；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不听毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管井就不自由。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远革命永进步一天不读主席书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干起工作劲不足；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两天不读主席书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇到困难顶不住；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三天不读主席书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘记过去阶级苦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长久不读主席书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁着眼睛走错路；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天都读主席书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远革命永进步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了两分法脑子里有了“两分法”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了成绩喜不倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇到困难吓不倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰了钉子弯不了。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}